<template>
    <v-form v-on:submit.prevent="submitForm">
      <v-text-field
        v-model="destination"
        label="Destination"
        required
      ></v-text-field>
      <v-row>
        <v-col cols="12" sm="6">
          <v-date-picker
            v-model="startDate"
            label="Start Date"
            required
          ></v-date-picker>

        <v-col cols="12" sm="6">
          <v-date-picker
            v-model="endDate"
            label="End Date"
            required
          ></v-date-picker>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
      <v-btn color="primary" type="submit">Submit</v-btn>
    </v-form>
  </template>
  
  <script>
  export default {
    data() {
      return {
        startDate: '',
        endDate: '',
        destination: ''
      }
    },
    methods: {
      submitForm() {
        // Handle form submission
        console.log('Start Date:', this.startDate)
        console.log('End Date:', this.endDate)
        console.log('Destination:', this.destination)
        // You can perform any other desired action with the form data here
      }
    }
  }
  </script>
  
  <style>
  /* Customize form styles here */
  </style>
